# List files or directories below to ignore them when running prettier
# More information: https://prettier.io/docs/en/ignore.html
#

**/staticresources/**
.localdevserver
.sfdx
.sf
.vscode

coverage/

# Salesforce metadata is authored by the platform, not by hand: `sf project
# retrieve` brings XML with expanded empty tags (`<x></x>`) which
# @prettier/plugin-xml collapses to `<x/>`, producing phantom diffs and false
# "local changes" that break source tracking on every retrieve. Metadata XML
# is therefore excluded from Prettier entirely. See issue #7.
**/*.xml

# CRM Analytics artifacts are platform-generated JSON (high conflict risk).
**/*.wdpr
**/*.wdf